By: Sri Ramakrishna
---
Ornaments cannot be made of pure gold. Some alloy must be mixed with it. A
man totally devoid of Maya will not survive more than twenty-one days. So
long as the man has a body, he must have some Maya, however small it may be,
to carry on the functions of the body.
